title: Russian Rave

Yesli ochenʹ zahotetʹ, mozhno v kosmos poletetʹ! 
Yesli ochenʹ zahotetʹ, mozhno v kosmos poletetʹ!

e ee eee

Rano utrom na rasvete, ya poĭdu k svoyeĭ rakete 
S chemodanchikom v rukah i so shlemom na plechah! 
Vzmashut lyudi mne rukami, provozhaya menya v putʹ dalʹniĭ 
YA polechu, kak yarkiĭ luch, sredi yarko-belyh tuch!
